{"tid":101361,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"【歌手2017】點睇哈薩克歌手Dimash！？","createTime":"2017-01-30T18:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T03:19:27.000Z","uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0db8db59af20ee040f2e2dfafa2871dcc9d9db","tid":101361,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:06:19.000Z","msg":"一個憂傷者的求救 &mdash;五大難唱法語歌&mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PjRhgSTyxDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPjRhgSTyxDc&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a8bd4d60\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PjRhgSTyxDc</a><br />\n<br />\nOpera2 &mdash;俄國海豚音王子Vitas著名歌曲&mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M7-twg8VHFE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM7-twg8VHFE&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a3707eff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M7-twg8VHFE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/99yJCVqhc80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F99yJCVqhc80&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1b0d6296\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/99yJCVqhc80</a><br />\n<br />\n天亮了&mdash;中文歌&mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yCEeleYG7Aw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyCEeleYG7Aw&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=504db4c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yCEeleYG7Aw</a>"},{"pid":"fbe080d8cf96b7aa8503c4eeacf54bb03f79186d","tid":101361,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:07:56.000Z","msg":"仲有佢之前唱第五元素又係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真今季冇人係佢嗰皮 就算有林憶蓮都係咁講"},{"pid":"91f35c7b215e03ef4a4ba34c0992e0fc6f1ab74b","tid":101361,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"先唔講佢嘅高音有幾癲<br />\n<br />\n淨係維持音準已經係賣點"},{"pid":"0aecc05585cf8ad21b13e7f36d0b6e470cc937bc","tid":101361,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:46:11.000Z","msg":"唔係連登冇人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674312936855cf41528ddbc6bfd4c3b56ffa7306","tid":101361,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"點解會有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8b50c07fdcf702ea7803d94f4c6cd969a03493","tid":101361,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:20:24.000Z","msg":"【版權？咩嚟㗎？】偷人首歌參加《歌手》仲拎去賣 迪瑪希涉侵權收律師信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170131/large/1485860060_bb98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170131%2Flarge%2F1485860060_bb98.jpg&h=1c661011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n版權？咩嚟0架？<br />\n<br />\n由《我是歌手》到依家改名做《歌手》&mdash;&mdash;有傳係因為禁韓令而改名，更有傳謂，湖南衛視其實冇買到版權。<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢個禁韓令下嘅《歌手》係老翻定正版？係禁韓定唔係禁韓，呢兩個問題已經唔係問題，最新嘅問題係，俾大會「高度讚揚」、譽為「進口小哥哥」嘅哈薩克代表迪瑪希，竟然涉侵權。<br />\n<br />\n事緣迪瑪希喺上期《歌手》比賽中，以一首烏克蘭裔歌唱家維塔斯（Vitas）成名之作《Opera 2》再贏no.1，連升三Key令唔識俄羅斯話嘅現場觀眾都激動流淚，果然不負「哈薩克國寶」之名，香港人熟悉嘅林憶蓮同佢恩師杜麗莎，排名都要靠邊站。贏咗no.1之後，迪瑪希喺噚晚嘅大陸賀年節目裡面，又唱一次。<br />\n<br />\n點知，今日俄羅斯製作人兼Vitas經理人普多夫金(Sergey-Pudovkin)，喺微博替Vitas發佈「維權聲明」&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 律師信，指迪瑪希已多次喺冇授權情況下改編、演唱Vitas嘅作品《Opera 2》，「已經嚴重損害了我方合法權益，我對此很痛心，希望通過法律途徑能讓此事得到合理的解決」，要求湖南衛視停止侵權行。<br />\n<br />\n不過其實真正有責任嘅，係迪瑪希同佢所屬唱片公司，事先應與Vitas經理人公司或唱片公司傾妥版權，而非「粒聲唔出予取予攜」。問題唔止咁，依家迪瑪希仲竟然，將佢翻唱嘅《Opera 2》版本擺上微博上賣，每首兩蚊人仔。<br />\n迪瑪希唔止係零食本，仲有錢賺添！<br />\n版權，咩嚟㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170131/56244398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170131%2F56244398&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ec2b20f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170131%2F56244398&h=61062818\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170131/56244398</a>"},{"pid":"20f4b20342ba495402a29386337653ff2da4359d","tid":101361,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【版權？咩嚟㗎？】偷人首歌參加《歌手》仲拎去賣 迪瑪希涉侵權收律師信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170131/large/1485860060_bb98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170131%2Flarge%2F1485860060_bb98.jpg&h=1c661011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n版權？咩嚟0架？<br />\n<br />\n由《我是歌手》到依家改名做《歌手》&mdash;&mdash;有傳係因為禁韓令而改名，更有傳謂，湖南衛視其實冇買到版權。<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢個禁韓令下嘅《歌手》係老翻定正版？係禁韓定唔係禁韓，呢兩個問題已經唔係問題，最新嘅問題係，俾大會「高度讚揚」、譽為「進口小哥哥」嘅哈薩克代表迪瑪希，竟然涉侵權。<br />\n<br />\n事緣迪瑪希喺上期《歌手》比賽中，以一首烏克蘭裔歌唱家維塔斯（Vitas）成名之作《Opera 2》再贏no.1，連升三Key令唔識俄羅斯話嘅現場觀眾都激動流淚，果然不負「哈薩克國寶」之名，香港人熟悉嘅林憶蓮同佢恩師杜麗莎，排名都要靠邊站。贏咗no.1之後，迪瑪希喺噚晚嘅大陸賀年節目裡面，又唱一次。<br />\n<br />\n點知，今日俄羅斯製作人兼Vitas經理人普多夫金(Sergey-Pudovkin)，喺微博替Vitas發佈「維權聲明」&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 律師信，指迪瑪希已多次喺冇授權情況下改編、演唱Vitas嘅作品《Opera 2》，「已經嚴重損害了我方合法權益，我對此很痛心，希望通過法律途徑能讓此事得到合理的解決」，要求湖南衛視停止侵權行。<br />\n<br />\n不過其實真正有責任嘅，係迪瑪希同佢所屬唱片公司，事先應與Vitas經理人公司或唱片公司傾妥版權，而非「粒聲唔出予取予攜」。問題唔止咁，依家迪瑪希仲竟然，將佢翻唱嘅《Opera 2》版本擺上微博上賣，每首兩蚊人仔。<br />\n迪瑪希唔止係零食本，仲有錢賺添！<br />\n版權，咩嚟㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170131/56244398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170131%2F56244398&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ec2b20f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170131%2F56244398&h=61062818\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170131/56244398</a></blockquote><br />\n責任不在歌手喎"},{"pid":"309cd0173792b70fb24622d84b55e09e9fd7b8f8","tid":101361,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:21:2